metadata.description: "Crow Clan is a collection of 1000 randomly generated and stylistically curated NFTs that exist on the Ethereum Blockchain. The “Crows Clan” is an NFT collection that highlights crypto security, hacking for the greater good, and the degen community making the crypto ecosystem safer for all. The Crow Collection is dedicated to our early supporters - depositors & contributors. Visit [https://hats.finance/nft] to learn more"
